com.pom.crimson.functions

Class GenericFunctionsAPI

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pom.crimson.functions.GenericFunctionsAPI

  • public class GenericFunctionsAPI
extends java.lang.Object
    GenericFunctionsAPI class contains: Functions related extracting profile data like profileId,contactType, archtypeId etc of profile Functions related to fetching related profiles data like fetching preferred name for Child,parent, Functions related to creating/deleting test data for profile: Create related contacts like Child,parent, Grandparent Functions related to fetching recommended content, daily tips etc Functions for extracting user groups.
    Author:
    Jaspreet Kaur Chagger
